file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: "Todo API"
  version: "1.0.0"
servers:
  - url: https://mytodos.doesnotexist/
    description: Core
paths:
  /todos: 
    get:
      description: Return a list of Todo entities
      operationId: todos_ListTodos
      parameters:
          - name: active
            in: query
            schema:
              type: boolean
          - name: keyword
            in: query
            schema:
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: collectionTodos
                type: object
                properties:
                  value:
                    type: array
                    items: 
                      $ref: "#/components/schemas/todo"

    post:
      requestBody:
        description: New Todo
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/todo'
        required: true
      responses:
        '201':
          description: OK
  /todos/{todoId}:
    get:
      description: Return a single Todo object
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
    delete:
      description: Delete a single Todo object
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
components:
  schemas:
    todo:
      title: Todo
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        subject:
          type: string
